@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_zrowsh(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.abs(((v2 + 0.03 - v2 + 0.58) + 0.53))
    v2 = (wp.cos(0.89) + wp.exp((v0 + 0.65 * v1 + 0.21)))
    tmp = wp.abs(0.14)
    tmp = (v1 / wp.exp((tmp + 0.68 / v1 + 0.08)))
    data[tid] = v0
